description: Gets the most recent message movement tasks (up to 10) under a specific source queue.

parameters.name: SourceArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the queue whose message movement tasks are to be listed.

nested_items.name: Results
nested_items.description: A list of message movement tasks and their attributes.

nested_items.name: TaskHandle
nested_items.description: An identifier associated with a message movement task. When this field is returned in the response of the ListMessageMoveTasks action, it is only populated for tasks that are in RUNNING status.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the message movement task. Possible values are: RUNNING, COMPLETED, CANCELLING, CANCELLED, and FAILED.

nested_items.name: SourceArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the queue that contains the messages to be moved to another queue.

nested_items.name: DestinationArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the destination queue if it has been specified in the StartMessageMoveTask request. If a DestinationArn has not been specified in the StartMessageMoveTask request, this field value will be NULL.

nested_items.name: MaxNumberOfMessagesPerSecond
nested_items.description: The number of messages to be moved per second (the message movement rate), if it has been specified in the StartMessageMoveTask request. If a MaxNumberOfMessagesPerSecond has not been specified in the StartMessageMoveTask request, this field value will be NULL.

nested_items.name: ApproximateNumberOfMessagesMoved
nested_items.description: The approximate number of messages already moved to the destination queue.

nested_items.name: ApproximateNumberOfMessagesToMove
nested_items.description: The number of messages to be moved from the source queue. This number is obtained at the time of starting the message movement task and is only included after the message movement task is selected to start.

nested_items.name: FailureReason
nested_items.description: The task failure reason (only included if the task status is FAILED).

nested_items.name: StartedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The timestamp of starting the message movement task.
